{"tid":1383428,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助] 因為梁天琦講既野 重新拾起改變深藍家人的念頭","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:23:35.000Z","uid":27718,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4c39d7daa58ce26d294536ce9f05dbce199630","tid":1383428,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"&quot;政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。&quot;<br />\n梁天琦<br />\n2019 年 7 月 26 日<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但梁天琦呀...我到底應該點做</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經想盡辦法等屋企睇到港台31 (屋企不在訊號範圍)，仲成日撳過去等佢地睇多啲！<br />\n但廳嗰兩件深藍都係死都要撳返去CCTVB新聞台...<br />\n<br />\n五年前起，關係已經變到好差<br />\n<br />\n今日喺某個撐警facebook page見到屋企嗰兩個深藍喺度Like入面啲post...<br />\n我whatsapp啲資訊畀佢地已經唔撚理我，直接無視<br />\n到底我應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n上星期因為森美講既野，已經逐漸放棄...<br />\n但今日又睇到梁天琦既信<br />\n我好矛盾，我應唔應該再徙口水去改變屋企既深藍?"},{"pid":"fdb7a8ece0ac5694c406c889fa443604d5f9e57b","tid":1383428,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"出唔到去嘅你都有野幫到手!<br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"98d8d7b29a93c324a2b58a8eb86cf10cc672be2c","tid":1383428,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d112711bdd387415535c69bb8829640c236033","tid":1383428,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"要無比EQ"},{"pid":"fc7e226a225e3952d721f4099379185e559bcd6a","tid":1383428,"uid":265152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"del左cctvb佢咪得"},{"pid":"c387d9f172899d73d414fa4